~~~ Flow ~~~
1. Tell user 5 tries.
2. Tell user number of letters.
3. First letter decides first letter of word.
4. Afterwards each guess will be correct or incorrect.
5. Show correct letters otherwise goto 6.
6. Show relevant warnings.
7. Show number of guesses left.
8. User loses.
~~~ Plan ~~~
1. A class Dictionary with an array of sorts of strings.
2. Size passed a parameter decided randomly each time.
3. Adds relevant words of that length.
4. Add these words to array of dict and check each guess.
5. Each guess check against possible words.
6. If there are any words without that letter return wrong
7. If there is minimize possible words to the most possible.
8. Repeat until player loses.
